<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:19:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国零售商因担心罢工和混乱而急于节日进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/us-retailers-rush-holiday-imports-fearing-strikes-disruptions-2024-08-09/</link><description>零售商正在推动今年夏季对美国的进口热潮，因为企业要防范潜在的港口工人罢工以及在假日购物季缩短之前红海袭击造成的持续运输中断。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/us-retailers-rush-holiday-imports-fearing-strikes-disruptions-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>全球石油需求需要更快增长才能消化 OPEC+ 的加息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/global-oil-demand-needs-rise-faster-absorb-opec-hike-2024-08-09/</link><description>数据、分析师和行业消息人士称，未来几个月全球石油需求增长需要加速，否则市场将难以消化 OPEC+ 计划从 10 月份开始增加的石油供应。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/global-oil-demand-needs-rise-faster-absorb-opec-hike-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求一些券商对债券交易进行合规检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国证券监管机构已下令一些券商检查其债券交易活动，当局试图遏制对中国政府债券的疯狂购买。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：动荡的一周以高点结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-09/</link><description>Stella Qiu 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 04:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，字节跳动寻求 50 亿美元贷款再融资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-seek-refinancing-5-bln-loan-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-09/</link><description>彭博社周五援引知情人士的话报道称，Tiktok 所有者字节跳动正准备在三年内为一笔 50 亿美元的贷款再融资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 04:23:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-seek-refinancing-5-bln-loan-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>从百事可乐到宝洁，印度成为下一个增长大赌注，而中国落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pepsico-pg-india-becomes-next-big-growth-bet-china-lags-2024-08-09/</link><description>印度已成为百事可乐、联合利华和其他包装食品巨头的下一个大赌注，这些巨头希望填补中国经济复苏不平衡留下的增长真空。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pepsico-pg-india-becomes-next-big-growth-bet-china-lags-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份降雨和洪水导致自然灾害损失近一倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国政府表示，7月份中国的极端降雨和严重洪涝导致自然灾害造成的经济损失比去年同期增加近一倍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>日本首相在地震风险警告后取消中亚之行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-weighs-cancelling-central-asia-trip-after-earthquake-warning-ntv-says-2024-08-09/</link><description>日本首相岸田文雄周五取消了访问中亚的计划，转而采取预防措施，此前史无前例地警告太平洋沿岸发生大地震的风险高于平常。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-weighs-cancelling-central-asia-trip-after-earthquake-warning-ntv-says-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市将以高位结束残酷的一周，日元承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-09/</link><description>亚洲股市在高位结束了艰难的一周，日本股市即将收复周一以来的所有巨额跌幅，而日元再次下滑，因为市场削弱了美国大幅降息的可能性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 02:19:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>天气因素导致中国消费价格上涨；国内需求依然疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</link><description>7月份中国消费者价格上涨速度略快于预期，部分原因是天气因素影响了食品供应，而生产者通货紧缩持续存在，使中国的基本消费趋势保持疲软，这是对政策制定者的考验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>就业救济后美元维持在一周高位附近；人民币攀升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-near-one-week-high-jobs-relief-yen-sags-2024-08-09/</link><description>周五，美元兑主要竞争对手徘徊在一周高位附近，美国初请失业金人数出现近一年来最大跌幅，缓解了人们对即将到来的经济衰退的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-near-one-week-high-jobs-relief-yen-sags-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称交易账户不得借用，中国国债下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</link><description>监管机构对中国炙手可热的债券市场涉嫌不当行为展开调查后，官方媒体表示交易账户不得借用或转让，中国国债周五下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:59:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>大熊猫栖息地在加州动物园大张旗鼓地开放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/giant-panda-habitat-opens-california-zoo-much-fanfare-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，圣地亚哥动物园的两只中国大熊猫在一场国际仪式上向公众开放，两只中国大熊猫现已成为加州居民。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 23:05:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/giant-panda-habitat-opens-california-zoo-much-fanfare-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：乐观情绪上升，但中国通胀迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-08/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大和澳大利亚瞄准中国，表示加强军事合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</link><description>加拿大和澳大利亚对中国对南海争议海域的主权声索表示震惊，周四表示，两国将加强军事和国防工业合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>